ith one parasite than two.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "57e9fa42-c492-477c-941f-5652d1a345ab"], "had6baf0dgb46cg4ea8g87d3g483e17939680": ["Yes - it was the right choice. Vampires are monsters, by any account.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "2a1e7462-1d15-45e7-8564-b18bc51e7b43"], "hf4b597bege7bcg4d73g80fdg6a83d6a59f4a": ["I find few things delightful. The surrender of Astarion is among them.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "2a1e7462-1d15-45e7-8564-b18bc51e7b43"], "h50773939g4ce1g48f5g83edgf391d7991715": ["Yes. Astarion was a liability. We did what we had to.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "2a1e7462-1d15-45e7-8564-b18bc51e7b43"], "hb4c407ecg35f1g42d1gb79bg03e15f180e46": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "2a1e7462-1d15-45e7-8564-b18bc51e7b43"], "h4fe70ed8g9985g4c7cg98f5g31d6ecb4cb62": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "2a1e7462-1d15-45e7-8564-b18bc51e7b43"], "hceee0d2eg7d43g4758gb216gc9431ccddf8e": ["| I agree. I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "2a1e7462-1d15-45e7-8564-b18bc51e7b43"], "h9b90a84ag2b43g42aegbc71gcd2597496b8f": ["| I agree. I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "2a1e7462-1d15-45e7-8564-b18bc51e7b43"], "h3d495f57gead7g4b88ga758g5