0b6g812dg490a92d38ca6": ["| We are in agreement: B. (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "6b7b55b1-f6f7-4944-8744-d5c562cd4440"], "hd6e7b27ag63c0g4500ga21bge3c685e10187": ["We made a mistake. I suppose only time will tell what's happened to him.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "6b7b55b1-f6f7-4944-8744-d5c562cd4440"], "h19754888g4a83g429fgb1f7gcf75c514a4c2": ["No - this was the right choice. Vampires are monsters, by any account.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "faf7d64a-9d09-4cf7-b114-e1a1d5f0650b"], "h6841aef4ge0edg4666g90e3g26e85f1d28f1": ["I find few things delightful. The surrender of Astarion is among them.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "faf7d64a-9d09-4cf7-b114-e1a1d5f0650b"], "hca44c8c7g53b8g454bg9647g09f38e092b99": ["No. Astarion was a liability. We did what we had to.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "faf7d64a-9d09-4cf7-b114-e1a1d5f0650b"], "h914099a0g7557g4b58g81e8ge3ccb97a4103": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "faf7d64a-9d09-4cf7-b114-e1a1d5f0650b"], "hb392ffbbg3c56g4cdbgbbe0g5be7549eb0fa": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.html", "faf7d64a-9d09-4cf7-b114-e1a1d5f0650b"], "hdf248d1cgf77cg4e11gaaafgd5d515d886d9": ["| I disagree. I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion.h